Introduction

Yebit is a South Korean singer-songwriter signed with Magic Strawberry Sound. She is known for sharing her song covers on her YouTube and SoundCloud platforms. Yebit made her debut as a solo artist on May 4, 2020, with the digital single "Smile for Me."
